WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.320 --> 02:49.980
[Episode 26]

02:50.240 --> 02:51.870
What do you want to tell me, Grandfather?

02:52.220 --> 02:53.829
A truth.

02:53.860 --> 02:56.210
It's the truth that you guys have been wanting to know,

02:57.020 --> 02:59.820
which is regarding the boy with purple eyes.

03:02.290 --> 03:04.080
25 years ago,

03:04.910 --> 03:06.280
Bai Ze

03:06.300 --> 03:08.370
was born with purple eyes.

03:16.710 --> 03:18.700
Just wait, don't fret.

03:19.220 --> 03:20.290
Congratulations to the Chief

03:20.320 --> 03:21.760
on welcoming two grandchildren.

03:22.690 --> 03:26.190
Congratulations to the Chief on welcoming two grandchildren!

03:26.640 --> 03:27.730
Congratulations.

03:32.230 --> 03:33.760
These purple eyes are from the heaven,

03:34.250 --> 03:35.850
so he must be extraordinary.

03:35.930 --> 03:37.480
From then on,

03:37.700 --> 03:39.100
I knew

03:39.510 --> 03:40.910
my grandson

03:40.940 --> 03:43.350
doesn't belong to me anymore.

03:45.480 --> 03:47.570
In the first few decades,

03:47.690 --> 03:49.410
besides a pair of purple eyes,

03:49.910 --> 03:51.660
Yue was no different

03:52.010 --> 03:53.730
from others.

03:54.390 --> 03:56.000
I told myself,

03:56.140 --> 03:58.230
maybe I was wrong.

03:58.670 --> 04:00.080
Maybe Yue

04:00.100 --> 04:03.380
just happened to have a pair of purple eyes.

04:04.640 --> 04:07.020
Afterwards, Yue and Qi Feng

04:07.200 --> 04:09.730
took it upon themselves to switch their eye colors.

04:10.780 --> 04:13.270
I was worried something might happen,

04:13.730 --> 04:16.410
but I didn't give them a hard time.

04:16.760 --> 04:18.079
Yue!

04:18.450 --> 04:20.839
One year later,

04:21.269 --> 04:23.510
when Yue went up to the mountain to collect some herbs,

04:23.820 --> 04:25.700
he fell off the cliff.

04:27.690 --> 04:28.690
Yue!

04:30.900 --> 04:31.820
Yue!

04:33.460 --> 04:34.420
Yue.

04:38.480 --> 04:39.400
Yue.

04:39.430 --> 04:40.190
Yue?

04:40.210 --> 04:42.050
I'm Grandfather.

04:43.960 --> 04:45.370
The inevitable

04:46.290 --> 04:48.159
has arrived.

04:48.790 --> 04:50.200
What does the

04:50.220 --> 04:51.340
purple forehead mark mean?

04:51.630 --> 04:54.940
That's the Demon Lord's Divine Mantle.

04:55.120 --> 04:57.240
That year when he fell off the cliff,

04:57.310 --> 04:58.140
Yue

04:58.170 --> 04:59.700
the Demon Lord

04:59.850 --> 05:02.910
finally possessed his body.

05:03.280 --> 05:04.680
You mean

05:05.030 --> 05:06.620
Fan Yue is the Demon Lord?

05:09.680 --> 05:11.730
Wasn't the Divine Race wiped out a long time ago?

05:12.160 --> 05:14.530
How could the Demon Lord descend into Fan Yue's body?

05:14.560 --> 05:16.170
How could we ever know

05:16.420 --> 05:19.700
the full story of what happened to the Divine Race?

05:19.850 --> 05:21.000
But no matter

05:21.020 --> 05:23.090
what the reason was,

05:23.420 --> 05:24.650
the Demon Lord

05:24.680 --> 05:26.390
is deeply indebted

05:26.600 --> 05:28.080
to the Bai Ze Clan.

05:28.560 --> 05:30.410
Our clan's mission

05:30.570 --> 05:33.490
is to protect the Demon Lord.

05:37.710 --> 05:40.150
Master, you want to force your way into Bai Shuo's sea of consciousness?

05:41.680 --> 05:43.240
These past few days,

05:44.140 --> 05:45.990
I've been wondering why she remained unharmed when absorbing Contemplations previously,

05:46.170 --> 05:47.770
but hasn't woken up this time.

05:48.220 --> 05:50.220
I think it’s related to the spirit of Bai Ze Clan.

05:50.740 --> 05:52.120
Bai Ze's spiritual soul?

05:52.370 --> 05:53.700
In ancient times,

05:53.890 --> 05:55.280
the ancestors of Bai Ze Clan

05:55.300 --> 05:57.120
were protected by Demon Lord Jing Yuan.

05:57.140 --> 05:59.270
They were even bestowed a sliver of divine power by the Demon Lord.

05:59.960 --> 06:01.460
Although tens of thousands of years have passed

06:01.570 --> 06:03.480
and the Bai Ze Clan's divine power may no longer be apparent,

06:03.750 --> 06:06.030
but the spiritual energy and soul in their blood

06:06.060 --> 06:07.800
remain stronger than those of ordinary demons.

06:08.020 --> 06:10.110
Otherwise, their spiritual soul would not have remained intact for years,

06:10.470 --> 06:11.530
leaving the Stone Clan no choice

06:11.670 --> 06:13.370
but to suppress them via a formation.

06:13.680 --> 06:15.270
Are you trying to say that

06:15.330 --> 06:16.980
the spiritual soul of the Bai Ze Clan

06:17.010 --> 06:17.890
is now

06:17.910 --> 06:19.500
in Bai Shuo's sea of consciousness,

06:19.530 --> 06:20.870
suppressing her willpower

06:21.040 --> 06:22.660
and causing her to not wake up?

06:22.750 --> 06:24.630
That's why I have to enter her sea of consciousness

06:25.280 --> 06:26.420
in order to wake her up.

06:26.440 --> 06:27.320
No, Master.

06:27.350 --> 06:28.520
It's too dangerous.

06:28.540 --> 06:30.780
One's spiritual consciousness is the weakest thing in the world.

06:30.810 --> 06:33.070
Once your spiritual consciousness dissipates, it means death.

06:33.130 --> 06:34.390
Even with your demonic power,

06:34.390 --> 06:36.730
it's not safe to enter someone else's sea of consciousness by force.

06:36.750 --> 06:37.920
If anything goes wrong,

06:37.950 --> 06:39.590
your spiritual soul will be swallowed

06:39.680 --> 06:41.090
and you will never wake up again.

06:41.110 --> 06:42.550
That's why we can't wait any longer.

06:42.580 --> 06:43.020
But...

06:43.040 --> 06:44.800
I am from the Bai Ze Clan.

06:44.980 --> 06:46.610
Shuo is the one I love.

06:46.920 --> 06:48.560
This time, I must go.

06:51.560 --> 06:53.190
I know I can't stop you.

06:53.220 --> 06:54.230
It is most dangerous when

06:54.250 --> 06:55.930
your spiritual consciousness leaves the body.

06:57.120 --> 06:58.570
I'll protect you from outside the room.

07:30.320 --> 07:33.810
♫The person standing far away♫

07:34.920 --> 07:36.620
♫Don't be afraid♫

07:37.800 --> 07:41.740
♫The stars will guide you to me♫

07:37.870 --> 07:38.870
Shuo.

07:40.690 --> 07:41.409
Wait for me.

07:42.600 --> 07:49.220
♫Walk towards me♫

07:51.040 --> 07:54.020
♫My heart feels so...♫

07:54.450 --> 07:57.400
♫It's pounding♫

07:54.960 --> 07:57.710
So when the Tiger Clan came to ask for the boy with purple eyes,

07:57.730 --> 07:59.730
you sacrificed Qi Feng

07:59.830 --> 08:01.180
in order to protect Demon Lord Fan Yue?

08:01.800 --> 08:04.550
I had let Qi Feng down.

08:05.680 --> 08:06.810
But if

08:07.630 --> 08:09.320
I had to do it all over again,

08:10.670 --> 08:11.610
I...

08:12.450 --> 08:15.520
will still make the same choice.

08:16.610 --> 08:18.940
This is both Qi Feng

08:19.690 --> 08:21.890
and Bai Ze's destiny.

08:25.710 --> 08:27.590
When I first entered this valley,

08:27.680 --> 08:29.410
I found it rather strange.

08:29.750 --> 08:31.780
Since the resentment of Bai Ze has been resolved,

08:32.000 --> 08:33.500
why is the valley

08:33.520 --> 08:35.919
still shrouded in such thick fog,

08:35.950 --> 08:37.470
never seeing the light of the day?

08:38.179 --> 08:39.390
Now, it seems that

08:39.700 --> 08:42.100
the fog is probably caused by you, Grandfather.

08:42.409 --> 08:44.720
It's because there's something you can't let go of in your heart

08:45.000 --> 08:47.450
that is causing this lingering sorrow.

08:47.480 --> 08:49.000
I don't regret

08:49.880 --> 08:51.570
what happened back then,

08:52.130 --> 08:53.420
but I feel guilty.

08:54.370 --> 08:55.700
I am the reason

08:55.730 --> 08:57.810
the two brothers

08:57.840 --> 08:59.790
ended up like this.

09:00.420 --> 09:01.990
That day,

09:02.760 --> 09:04.680
it was my choice

09:04.700 --> 09:07.870
that changed their respective destinies,

09:08.970 --> 09:10.480
forcing them to

09:10.520 --> 09:13.530
walk down separate but difficult roads.

09:14.890 --> 09:17.130
As the Chief of Bai Ze Clan,

09:17.150 --> 09:18.790
I can't regret it.

09:19.450 --> 09:21.900
But as their grandfather,

09:22.450 --> 09:25.140
I feel guilty towards these two children.

09:25.890 --> 09:27.050
Especially...

09:27.440 --> 09:28.490
Qi Feng.

09:29.510 --> 09:31.730
They were both born on the same day,

09:32.000 --> 09:34.900
but because he doesn't have the Demon Lord's Divine Mantle,

09:35.280 --> 09:36.920
he's destined

09:36.940 --> 09:38.770
to be sacrificed.

09:40.440 --> 09:42.040
If I were him,

09:42.880 --> 09:44.670
I would also grow hateful too.

09:44.940 --> 09:47.300
But Yue did nothing wrong.

09:47.330 --> 09:49.000
The moment he was born,

09:49.020 --> 09:50.920
he was bestowed

09:50.940 --> 09:52.820
the destiny of the Demon Lord.

09:52.850 --> 09:55.320
He too had no choice.

09:55.510 --> 09:57.130
I hope that

09:57.150 --> 09:59.000
they would hate me

10:00.160 --> 10:01.460
instead of

10:01.780 --> 10:03.950
hating each other.

10:07.370 --> 10:08.790
If only Qi Feng could hear

10:08.790 --> 10:10.750
what you just said, Grandfather.

10:12.370 --> 10:13.370
Fan Yue?

10:28.890 --> 10:30.040
Yue!

10:36.970 --> 10:37.660
Grandfather.

11:24.570 --> 11:26.060
I'll say it again.

11:26.090 --> 11:29.250
Hand over the child with purple eyes!

11:30.720 --> 11:31.880
Qi Feng,

11:32.090 --> 11:33.430
you must remember.

11:33.810 --> 11:34.950
Yue

11:35.060 --> 11:36.810
was born extraordinary.

11:37.370 --> 11:39.950
He is not only your brother,

11:40.290 --> 11:41.860
he is someone

11:41.880 --> 11:45.010
you have to protect with your life.

11:45.150 --> 11:46.980
I can help you,

11:47.010 --> 11:48.250
but I don't like

11:48.440 --> 11:50.200
people who are weak.

11:51.730 --> 11:53.420
If it takes blood

11:53.450 --> 11:55.530
to soothe the hatred in your heart

11:55.560 --> 11:57.520
and bring back the Qi Feng of the past,

11:59.700 --> 12:01.880
once I finish what I need to do,

12:02.990 --> 12:04.070
I'll give you

12:05.790 --> 12:06.770
my life.

12:07.960 --> 12:10.440
Although I didn't see the face of the mysterious man,

12:10.470 --> 12:11.670
I saw a black snake mark

12:11.670 --> 12:13.390
on his arm.

12:22.460 --> 12:24.000
You've overestimated yourself.

12:24.200 --> 12:25.800
You are lucky to even be alive,

12:25.820 --> 12:27.270
yet you came seeking your death?

12:27.350 --> 12:29.120
I know I can't beat you,

12:29.140 --> 12:31.260
and I know I might die here.

12:31.290 --> 12:32.280
But I must seek vengeance for

12:32.310 --> 12:33.240
the extermination of my clan

12:33.260 --> 12:34.280
and the death of my father!

12:34.310 --> 12:35.590
Extermination of your clan?

12:36.140 --> 12:37.930
Exactly who destroyed whose clan,

12:37.950 --> 12:39.670
and who owes whose revenge?

12:39.700 --> 12:41.570
My father might not be a good person,

12:42.220 --> 12:43.860
but he is a good father.

12:43.890 --> 12:45.230
As his daughter,

12:45.260 --> 12:46.550
this is something I must do.

12:52.750 --> 12:54.270
Why stay alive

12:55.860 --> 12:57.580
if it hurts this much?

13:06.850 --> 13:07.640
Forget it.

13:07.750 --> 13:09.420
Someone doesn't want me to kill you.

13:10.020 --> 13:11.750
I'll spare your life today.

13:13.880 --> 13:14.800
[Qi Feng]

13:26.460 --> 13:27.610
It’s all my fault.

13:28.700 --> 13:30.800
If I hadn't left Bai Ze Clan back then,

13:31.280 --> 13:33.280
I might have met Qi Feng when he came back

13:33.450 --> 13:35.100
and stopped the Stone Clan from trespassing.

13:35.540 --> 13:37.270
This way, Qi Feng wouldn't have been consumed by hatred,

13:38.020 --> 13:39.420
and the people of our clan wouldn't be so resentful.

13:44.510 --> 13:47.630
Don't take everything upon yourself.

13:47.660 --> 13:48.610
Yue,

13:48.630 --> 13:49.860
you've already been through enough

13:49.880 --> 13:52.040
all these years.

13:52.060 --> 13:53.170
Grandfather,

13:53.370 --> 13:55.180
do you really think I'm Demon Lord?

13:55.720 --> 13:57.520
But I don't have any relevant memories.

13:57.690 --> 13:59.000
Sometimes,

13:59.060 --> 14:01.260
that's just how destiny unfolds itself.

14:01.280 --> 14:03.440
It happens when you least expect it.

14:03.460 --> 14:05.580
When it hits,

14:05.610 --> 14:07.490
if there's no way of avoiding it,

14:07.520 --> 14:09.920
you have to face it head on.

14:10.330 --> 14:11.610
Grandfather,

14:11.630 --> 14:13.040
you seem to have something else in mind.

14:13.070 --> 14:14.890
This is exactly why

14:14.920 --> 14:17.040
why I had to connect with you.

14:17.540 --> 14:18.920
The Bai Ze Clan,

14:19.200 --> 14:21.820
descended from ancient divine beasts,

14:21.850 --> 14:24.400
gathers the spiritual energy of heaven and earth into their very being.

14:24.420 --> 14:26.010
Every Chief

14:26.030 --> 14:28.200
have the power of prophecy.

14:28.230 --> 14:29.540
We can see

14:29.560 --> 14:31.380
major events of the future.

14:31.730 --> 14:32.690
Major events?

14:33.300 --> 14:34.710
Not long ago,

14:34.740 --> 14:36.900
I had a premonition.

14:37.550 --> 14:39.410
The resurrection of the Hidden Lord

14:39.480 --> 14:41.770
will cause a catastrophe in the world.

14:41.790 --> 14:43.540
Resurrection of the Hidden Lord?

14:43.680 --> 14:45.250
Like you,

14:45.270 --> 14:46.580
there is someone destined

14:46.610 --> 14:48.210
to become the Hidden Lord.

14:48.750 --> 14:49.630
But...

14:49.650 --> 14:51.500
I don't know who this person might be,

14:51.730 --> 14:52.850
nor do I know

14:52.870 --> 14:54.310
where he is.

14:54.750 --> 14:55.790
The only thing

14:55.810 --> 14:57.510
I am sure is that

14:57.530 --> 15:00.070
once the Hidden Lord reappears,

15:00.340 --> 15:02.680
the Eastern Continent will be destroyed.

15:08.120 --> 15:09.250
What happened?

15:11.170 --> 15:12.360
Don't panic.

15:16.180 --> 15:18.270
Nothing happened.

15:18.800 --> 15:19.840
It's just that...

15:19.860 --> 15:21.860
the time has come.

15:22.620 --> 15:24.450
Bai Ze's Hatred Contemplation

15:24.470 --> 15:26.110
has been resolved.

15:26.550 --> 15:27.960
This illusion

15:28.120 --> 15:30.330
will naturally collapse.

15:30.640 --> 15:32.590
My clansmen and I

15:32.960 --> 15:34.630
should leave.

15:35.430 --> 15:36.190
Grandfather.

15:36.850 --> 15:37.970
Where are you going?

15:40.130 --> 15:42.060
The Bai Ze Clan,

15:42.330 --> 15:44.200
born of heaven and earth,

15:44.570 --> 15:47.110
should of course return to the heaven and earth.

15:48.000 --> 15:48.950
Yue,

15:49.400 --> 15:50.980
there's no need to regret

15:51.560 --> 15:53.010
or hold on to it.

15:53.720 --> 15:54.690
You...

15:54.720 --> 15:56.070
have your own destiny.

15:56.440 --> 15:59.880
Don’t be trapped in the past.

16:04.400 --> 16:05.640
The Bai Ze Clan

16:05.660 --> 16:07.880
have one last present

16:07.910 --> 16:09.190
for

16:09.210 --> 16:10.450
Shuo.

16:10.950 --> 16:14.280
The entire Bai Ze Clan's final spiritual powers

16:14.300 --> 16:16.080
shall be given to you as our blessings.

16:16.660 --> 16:17.580
Here's wishing you

16:17.610 --> 16:19.950
a smooth acquisition of the Hatred Contemplation.

16:20.550 --> 16:21.940
May you

16:21.980 --> 16:24.160
never suffer in difficult times,

16:24.490 --> 16:25.980
and may every danger

16:26.050 --> 16:27.660
be turned into a path of ease.

16:30.490 --> 16:33.880
♫Across thousands of miles♫

16:38.910 --> 16:43.380
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

16:46.190 --> 16:53.130
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

16:54.640 --> 16:59.200
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

17:04.540 --> 17:09.030
♫The flowers flew away♫

17:12.260 --> 17:17.470
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

17:14.810 --> 17:16.030
Yue.

17:16.099 --> 17:17.619
Remember,

17:18.470 --> 17:20.960
don't be trapped in the past.

17:20.490 --> 17:27.010
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

17:27.930 --> 17:32.950
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

17:37.930 --> 17:39.720
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

17:39.910 --> 17:41.230
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

17:41.530 --> 17:43.350
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

17:43.870 --> 17:44.830
Let's go, Shuo.

17:44.130 --> 17:45.230
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

17:45.710 --> 17:47.230
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

17:46.790 --> 17:47.990
We should leave too.

17:47.710 --> 17:49.510
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

17:49.840 --> 17:51.670
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

17:52.010 --> 17:53.640
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

17:54.210 --> 17:55.750
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

17:56.110 --> 17:58.170
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

17:58.470 --> 17:59.990
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

18:00.500 --> 18:03.780
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

18:31.930 --> 18:35.590
♫The stars light up your eyes♫

18:35.570 --> 18:36.470
What's wrong?

18:38.260 --> 18:39.220
Nothing.

18:39.360 --> 18:42.000
♫You are my distant call♫

18:40.740 --> 18:42.240
I just want to hug you,

18:42.580 --> 18:43.780
and hug you tight.

18:43.330 --> 18:47.530
♫You are my first and last♫

18:44.710 --> 18:46.790
I'm afraid I won't be able to hug you in the very next moment.

18:48.350 --> 18:53.860
♫My heart is trembling for you♫

18:51.160 --> 18:53.380
This is the first time I've ever heard you speak words of affection.

18:54.670 --> 18:57.460
♫In this moment where we embrace each other♫

18:55.120 --> 18:56.280
How about...

18:56.630 --> 18:57.760
you say it again?

18:58.390 --> 19:02.840
♫Let's never let go♫

19:01.290 --> 19:03.070
I'm not joking with you.

19:03.450 --> 19:04.780
Neither am I.

19:09.310 --> 19:11.270
All this talk of the Demon Lord and Demon King...

19:12.460 --> 19:14.460
Sometimes I just wish I could leave it all behind

19:14.860 --> 19:16.740
and live secluded in the mountains with you,

19:17.390 --> 19:18.710
where we live freely with ease.

19:21.460 --> 19:23.130
The Divine Mantle of the Demon Lord

19:23.190 --> 19:24.380
is set by heaven.

19:25.950 --> 19:27.350
But it's up to you

19:27.700 --> 19:28.830
to decide who you want to be.

19:35.290 --> 19:36.160
What?

19:36.890 --> 19:38.230
Do you really want to live in seclusion with me?

19:39.210 --> 19:40.280
I just hope that

19:40.310 --> 19:42.680
you won't be caught up in the Demon Lord's Divine Mantle.

19:42.930 --> 19:44.300
If the world is peaceful,

19:44.990 --> 19:46.490
what's wrong with living in seclusion?

19:47.290 --> 19:49.140
But if what Grandfather said is true,

19:49.430 --> 19:50.850
where the resurrection of the Hidden Lord

19:50.880 --> 19:52.550
will cause a catastrophe in the world,

19:53.160 --> 19:54.920
where else can we hide?

19:57.280 --> 19:58.600
Fan Yue.

19:58.980 --> 20:00.090
Promise me.

20:00.700 --> 20:02.030
No matter

20:02.060 --> 20:03.770
what turmoil may come in the future,

20:03.790 --> 20:05.400
we shall face it together.

20:07.450 --> 20:08.370
Okay?

20:15.280 --> 20:16.100
Master.

20:17.370 --> 20:18.020
Come in.

20:28.070 --> 20:28.750
What is it?

20:29.850 --> 20:30.890
Chen Ye is missing.

20:53.050 --> 20:54.050
Greetings, Master.

20:54.460 --> 20:55.610
I’m useless.

20:55.640 --> 20:57.160
The plan with the Stone Clan failed,

20:57.180 --> 20:58.700
and I did not manage to kill Fan Yue

20:59.100 --> 21:01.430
or bring Bai Shuo and the Contemplation Stone back for you.

21:01.470 --> 21:02.780
Please punish me.

21:02.800 --> 21:05.220
The matter of the Stone Clan has been settled for a few days.

21:06.230 --> 21:07.700
Since you were injured,

21:07.880 --> 21:09.680
why didn't you come back until today?

21:09.700 --> 21:11.830
I was captured by Fan Yue and brought back to the Bright Moon Palace.

21:11.860 --> 21:14.620
I only had a chance to escape from Bright Moon Palace today.

21:14.850 --> 21:15.890
Once I was free,

21:15.920 --> 21:17.630
I came back to see you immediately.

21:19.960 --> 21:21.910
He didn't kill you,

21:21.930 --> 21:23.780
but just captured you alive?

21:23.880 --> 21:25.210
Fan Yue harbors sinister intentions.

21:25.230 --> 21:26.310
He wanted to

21:26.340 --> 21:28.190
find out more about your technique's weaknesses

21:28.330 --> 21:30.370
and the deployment of guards in Cold Spring Palace from me.

21:30.400 --> 21:32.360
How could I ever betray you?

21:32.380 --> 21:34.280
Although I didn't kill Fan Yue,

21:34.310 --> 21:35.630
I killed Cang Shan instead.

21:36.150 --> 21:37.390
The wounds on my body

21:37.780 --> 21:39.600
were inflicted by Fan Yue in his rage.

21:39.650 --> 21:41.200
You killed Cang Shan?

21:41.720 --> 21:42.440
Yes.

21:42.800 --> 21:43.420
Great.

21:46.190 --> 21:47.510
It's just a failure.

21:47.540 --> 21:48.570
You don't have to worry about it.

21:48.710 --> 21:50.080
By killing Cang Shan,

21:50.530 --> 21:51.880
you've managed to help me

21:51.900 --> 21:53.310
get rid of Fan Yue's right-hand man.

21:53.340 --> 21:54.280
You deserve credit.

21:54.310 --> 21:54.980
Come.

21:55.000 --> 21:55.770
Get up.

21:58.040 --> 21:59.350
I'll make them pay

21:59.370 --> 22:00.130
for the harm

22:00.160 --> 22:01.570
you've suffered.

22:02.190 --> 22:03.140
Thank you, Master.

22:31.190 --> 22:32.310
Idiot.

22:32.430 --> 22:34.250
Do you really think I can't tell

22:34.440 --> 22:36.090
that you're not hurt at all?

22:37.160 --> 22:39.090
I just wanted to see

22:39.110 --> 22:41.040
what you are trying to do.

22:41.680 --> 22:42.980
But Chen Ye,

22:43.020 --> 22:44.930
I was the one who saved your life,

22:45.040 --> 22:46.430
raised you,

22:46.620 --> 22:48.160
and taught you demonic magic.

22:48.210 --> 22:49.540
I'm very curious as to

22:50.500 --> 22:52.610
why you would want to kill me.

22:53.820 --> 22:56.280
Back then, it was you who got Tiger Clan to kill Bai Ze.

22:56.500 --> 22:59.050
It was you who wanted to find the boy with purple eyes.

22:59.400 --> 23:00.560
How did you know?

23:00.580 --> 23:03.040
The man who gave Tiger King the order to kill Bai Ze

23:03.320 --> 23:05.550
had a black snake mark on his arm.

23:07.260 --> 23:08.260
It seems

23:08.290 --> 23:09.680
there are still remnants of the Tiger Clan

23:09.700 --> 23:10.800
left in this world.

23:11.240 --> 23:12.040
That's right.

23:12.940 --> 23:14.220
I was the one who

23:14.250 --> 23:15.260
gave the order to kill Bai Ze

23:15.290 --> 23:16.350
back in the past.

23:16.670 --> 23:17.860
So what?

23:18.150 --> 23:19.320
If it weren't for me,

23:19.340 --> 23:21.250
how could you get to where you are today?

23:21.850 --> 23:22.720
What's wrong with

23:22.740 --> 23:23.630
being second to only one

23:23.660 --> 23:24.620
while being above everyone else

23:24.640 --> 23:26.370
here in Cold Spring Palace?

23:26.520 --> 23:27.590
Are those cheap lives

23:27.610 --> 23:28.970
from Bai Ze Clan

23:29.000 --> 23:30.610
deserving of you to disobey me?

23:30.630 --> 23:32.210
Their lives are not cheap!

23:39.890 --> 23:42.370
Back then, you brought me back from Baize Clan

23:42.860 --> 23:44.210
and raised me.

23:44.960 --> 23:47.280
All these years, you didn't kill me.

23:48.150 --> 23:49.960
That means you can't kill me.

23:51.200 --> 23:52.970
But one day,

23:53.210 --> 23:54.670
I'll be able to kill you.

24:14.300 --> 24:15.460
Everything you have now

24:15.490 --> 24:17.250
was given to you by me.

24:17.650 --> 24:18.500
Do you really think

24:18.530 --> 24:19.910
you can kill me...

24:30.920 --> 24:32.220
Impressive.

24:32.520 --> 24:34.630
You actually put poison

24:34.650 --> 24:37.440
into the power I gave you.

24:37.530 --> 24:39.050
Such ruthlessness,

24:39.080 --> 24:40.290
you truly

24:40.310 --> 24:41.900
are my disciple.

24:42.560 --> 24:43.770
But don't forget,

24:43.790 --> 24:45.950
I'm your master after all.

24:46.060 --> 24:47.230
Your poison

24:47.260 --> 24:48.460
can't hurt me.

24:48.860 --> 24:50.300
Kill me.

24:50.850 --> 24:53.120
Killing you would be too easy.

24:55.760 --> 24:56.870
I...

24:57.420 --> 24:59.610
suddenly want to clarify something.

25:00.470 --> 25:02.060
Since you know

25:02.090 --> 25:04.690
I’m the one who killed Bai Ze,

25:04.720 --> 25:06.000
why didn't you

25:06.020 --> 25:08.500
wan to join hands with me to kill Fan Yue,

25:08.530 --> 25:10.660
but instead came back to seek your death?

25:11.840 --> 25:13.280
Given Fan Yue's character,

25:13.300 --> 25:14.810
how could he have

25:14.840 --> 25:16.420
spared your life

25:16.660 --> 25:18.900
when you killed Cang Shan?

25:25.100 --> 25:25.860
Nuo.

25:25.890 --> 25:27.230
Why are you in the secret chamber?

25:27.250 --> 25:28.110
Where is Chen Ye?

25:30.260 --> 25:31.820
You were the one who opened the secret chamber.

25:32.610 --> 25:34.220
You were trying to kill him for revenge, right?

25:34.250 --> 25:36.080
He killed my father and my clan.

25:36.250 --> 25:37.760
Your father and your clansmen

25:37.790 --> 25:39.280
also have the blood of other tribes on their hands.

25:39.330 --> 25:41.440
The people they've killed also have their own loved ones.

25:41.560 --> 25:43.390
What's the point of your father saving you

25:43.410 --> 25:45.110
if you only know how to stop killing with even more killing?

25:48.600 --> 25:50.440
Chen Ye has escaped from Bright Moon Palace.

25:50.470 --> 25:52.030
It seems he went back to the Cold Spring Palace.

25:52.570 --> 25:54.490
It looks like he still wouldn't turn around.

25:55.300 --> 25:57.070
He still chose to be loyal to Zhen Yu.

25:57.820 --> 25:59.690
It's the path he chose for himself.

26:00.270 --> 26:01.640
You've done a great job.

26:06.270 --> 26:07.030
What's wrong?

26:07.760 --> 26:08.390
He...

26:08.410 --> 26:10.450
broke into your sea of consciousness by force.

26:10.480 --> 26:11.870
I’m afraid he had hurt his spiritual soul.

26:24.120 --> 26:25.800
Bai Ze Clan,

26:26.140 --> 26:27.620
purple-eyed boy,

26:28.400 --> 26:29.570
the Human Race,

26:29.590 --> 26:30.980
Ning'an City,

26:31.010 --> 26:32.220
and the Bai family.

26:36.270 --> 26:38.090
The Old Turtle predicted that

26:38.120 --> 26:40.000
one of the child is from Bai Ze Clan,

26:40.020 --> 26:42.590
and the other is from the Human Race.

26:42.620 --> 26:45.190
So, I brought back Qi Feng and Bai Xi.

26:46.160 --> 26:48.120
One was born with purple eyes,

26:48.580 --> 26:50.990
and the other was born with innate spiritual energy.

27:01.620 --> 27:03.210
They absorbed the Contemplation Stone

27:03.240 --> 27:04.680
and acquired the Outlander King's Sword.

27:05.360 --> 27:07.660
Bai Shuo is the child I was looking for.

27:08.920 --> 27:10.640
Since Fu Ling was mistakenly identified,

27:11.590 --> 27:12.870
could it be that Chen Ye,

27:13.660 --> 27:15.660
who has been by my side all these years

27:15.690 --> 27:19.030
without showing even a trace of divine energy,

27:19.340 --> 27:20.890
is also the wrong one?

27:21.450 --> 27:23.320
But he has purple eyes.

27:24.810 --> 27:27.550
What's the relationship between Fan Yue and Chen Ye?

27:27.680 --> 27:29.840
Why did he spare Chen Ye?

27:30.650 --> 27:33.790
Could there be some connection between Fan Yue and the Bai Ze Clan?

27:35.450 --> 27:37.350
Could it be that he is...

27:40.700 --> 27:41.650
These are calming pills;

27:41.680 --> 27:42.730
take them all.

27:43.670 --> 27:45.320
Don't be so tense.

27:45.600 --> 27:47.560
I just lost a bit of my spiritual soul.

27:47.580 --> 27:49.180
I'll be fine after some rest and recovery.

27:49.350 --> 27:50.590
The Demon Lord's divine power is boundless,

27:50.590 --> 27:51.720
and they live as long as the heavens;

27:51.720 --> 27:52.900
I shouldn't have worried.

27:54.530 --> 27:55.430
Are you angry?

27:56.160 --> 27:58.820
You know that venturing into the sea of consciousness would damage the spiritual soul,

27:58.850 --> 28:00.420
so why did you still do it?

28:00.840 --> 28:02.800
It's like you're worried about me.

28:02.820 --> 28:04.930
I can't stand by and watch you get hurt either.

28:04.960 --> 28:06.250
Don't talk about losing my spiritual soul,

28:06.280 --> 28:07.360
even if it's...

28:08.730 --> 28:10.290
Don't say anything ominous.

28:15.200 --> 28:16.750
Are you worried about something

28:17.830 --> 28:19.960
because of my Demon Lord's Divine Mantle?

28:23.050 --> 28:23.940
Shuo.

28:24.760 --> 28:26.100
I'm still Fan Yue,

28:26.530 --> 28:28.050
and nothing will change that.

28:28.830 --> 28:31.390
But the deity is really too far away from me.

28:32.590 --> 28:33.790
I'm afraid that

28:33.180 --> 28:37.290
♫Writing wishes in the night sky♫

28:34.240 --> 28:36.070
one day, whether you want to or not,

28:36.440 --> 28:38.750
you will become that Demon Lord, Jing Yuan, again.

28:37.960 --> 28:41.880
♫The clouds seal their approval for me♫

28:39.360 --> 28:40.440
I am Fan Yue,

28:41.060 --> 28:42.780
and no one can change that,

28:42.420 --> 28:46.150
♫You walk towards me slowly♫

28:43.490 --> 28:44.670
not even myself.

28:47.190 --> 28:49.960
♫Time stops♫

28:48.340 --> 28:49.310
Don't be afraid.

28:50.490 --> 28:51.970
No matter what the future is,

28:51.450 --> 28:55.520
♫The brightest star in the night sky♫

28:53.230 --> 28:54.040
I'm by your side.

28:55.980 --> 28:59.800
♫Is willing to extinguish for you♫

28:58.350 --> 28:59.810
Can you stop being angry?

29:00.360 --> 29:03.650
♫Because the starlight in your eyes♫

29:01.430 --> 29:02.940
Who said I'm not angry?

29:04.030 --> 29:05.190
Take the pills.

29:04.540 --> 29:08.910
♫Lights up my long night♫

29:05.250 --> 29:06.880
As long as your spiritual soul hasn't recovered,

29:06.910 --> 29:08.460
you're not allowed to leave the Bright Moon Palace.

29:11.520 --> 29:15.360
♫I'm afraid tomorrow is too far♫

29:15.810 --> 29:19.710
♫Love you at every moment♫

29:20.840 --> 29:21.850
♫Don't miss me♫

29:22.860 --> 29:24.070
♫I'll always be by your side♫

29:23.920 --> 29:25.120
How is Master Fan?

29:25.140 --> 29:25.980
He should be fine.

29:26.370 --> 29:27.890
I just gave him the pills.

29:29.090 --> 29:30.880
No matter whose divine mantle is on him,

29:31.430 --> 29:33.060
in my heart, he is Fan Yue,

29:33.350 --> 29:34.830
the only one I pledge loyalty to.

29:35.590 --> 29:37.150
You hear

29:37.660 --> 29:38.660
what I said to Fan Yue just now?

29:41.500 --> 29:42.230
By the way,

29:42.410 --> 29:44.540
I haven't had the chance to tell you since we returned.

29:44.920 --> 29:47.090
Master Fan asked me to look into Bai Xi's whereabouts.

29:47.750 --> 29:48.630
I found out that

29:48.890 --> 29:51.450
the Taoist who took her from the Bai family ten years ago

29:51.580 --> 29:53.460
is most likely from Cold Spring Palace.

29:58.090 --> 30:00.000
I saw Xi

30:00.150 --> 30:01.600
in Chen Ye's memories as well.

30:02.060 --> 30:04.670
Zhen Yu took Chen Ye away from the Bai Ze Clan

30:04.760 --> 30:07.050
because he thought he had the Demon Lord's Divine Mantle.

30:07.250 --> 30:09.420
But Bai Xi is just from Human Race;

30:09.590 --> 30:12.090
why would he go to such lengths to take her away?

30:13.230 --> 30:14.240
Don't be impulsive.

30:14.610 --> 30:16.050
All we know now is that

30:16.080 --> 30:17.920
Bai Xi was once in Cold Spring Palace.

30:18.030 --> 30:19.230
But all these years,

30:19.260 --> 30:20.410
I've never heard of anyone like her

30:20.430 --> 30:21.660
in the Cold Spring Palace.

30:21.850 --> 30:23.370
Zhen Yu must have hidden her away.

30:23.400 --> 30:25.020
If we rush over, we won't be able to find her.

30:26.100 --> 30:27.210
Let's wait

30:27.240 --> 30:28.540
until Master Fan recovers before we do anything.

30:51.800 --> 30:54.700
[Qi Feng]

31:10.330 --> 31:12.890
I didn't expect that the mighty Lord Chen Ye

31:12.910 --> 31:14.590
would have such a humiliating moment.

31:15.680 --> 31:16.870
I never thought

31:17.510 --> 31:20.470
the only one who would come to see me in the Cold Spring Palace would be you.

31:21.580 --> 31:22.570
What?

31:23.280 --> 31:24.560
Are you here to laugh at me?

31:25.490 --> 31:26.850
I'm not here to laugh at you.

31:27.220 --> 31:29.680
After all, who hasn't been here before?

31:30.030 --> 31:31.380
I'm just curious.

31:31.410 --> 31:32.720
You, who always avoids danger

31:32.720 --> 31:33.760
and is so loyal to him,

31:33.790 --> 31:35.830
why would you want to kill him and seek death?

31:36.210 --> 31:38.060
Don't you want him to die?

31:38.920 --> 31:40.440
You just don't dare to do it.

31:40.890 --> 31:42.530
So what if I want?

31:42.560 --> 31:44.400
My life is in his hands.

31:44.420 --> 31:45.550
Whether I betray him or not,

31:45.580 --> 31:47.210
what difference does it make to me?

31:47.530 --> 31:48.850
There are some things

31:49.350 --> 31:50.900
that are more important than life.

31:52.060 --> 31:54.630
The one who instructed the Tiger Clan to kill Bai Ze back then

31:55.310 --> 31:56.850
was Zhen Yu.

31:57.850 --> 31:59.300
Did you kill Master

31:59.320 --> 32:00.810
for revenge?

32:02.400 --> 32:03.840
Why did he do that?

32:03.890 --> 32:04.900
I don't know.

32:05.910 --> 32:07.240
All I know is that

32:07.460 --> 32:08.660
he brought me back

32:09.250 --> 32:11.170
because of my purple eyes.

32:11.850 --> 32:12.920
Purple eyes?

32:13.160 --> 32:14.560
Why haven't I seen them before?

32:14.730 --> 32:16.710
That's because Grandfather used sorcery

32:16.730 --> 32:18.410
to hide my purple eyes.

32:18.920 --> 32:20.580
Only Zhen Yu can see it.

32:25.110 --> 32:27.170
Why is Xi in your memory?

32:27.200 --> 32:28.880
Why is she in Cold Spring Palace?

32:29.070 --> 32:30.350
What Xi?

32:30.460 --> 32:31.790
The girl who was with you in the hall

32:31.810 --> 32:33.400
when you received your name from Zhen Yu.

32:33.430 --> 32:34.350
Where is she?

32:36.600 --> 32:37.700
Fu Ling,

32:38.240 --> 32:40.000
do you still remember your origins?

32:41.480 --> 32:42.640
What are you trying to say?

32:43.490 --> 32:45.490
Zhen Yu is unpredictable

32:45.510 --> 32:46.930
and full of schemes.

32:47.270 --> 32:48.620
Since he took me as his disciple

32:48.640 --> 32:50.330
because of my purple eyes,

32:51.660 --> 32:52.740
what about you?

32:53.330 --> 32:54.810
There are countless demons,

32:55.010 --> 32:56.670
and you're neither the most talented

32:56.700 --> 32:58.030
nor the strongest.

32:58.260 --> 32:59.850
Why did he take you in

32:59.870 --> 33:00.860
and keep you by his side?

33:02.040 --> 33:03.440
Aren't you curious

33:03.670 --> 33:05.500
who you were

33:05.920 --> 33:07.030
before you became Fu Ling?

33:11.910 --> 33:13.860
I'm not as curious as you.

33:13.890 --> 33:14.870
Sometimes,

33:14.890 --> 33:16.170
the more a man knows,

33:16.200 --> 33:17.810
the faster he will die.

33:17.830 --> 33:18.700
Just like you.

33:20.920 --> 33:21.870
True.

33:24.770 --> 33:25.920
You didn't come here

33:26.080 --> 33:28.490
just to ask me why I want to kill Zhen Yu, did you?

33:30.580 --> 33:31.650
Do you have the antidote

33:31.680 --> 33:32.720
for the Heart Devouring Pill?

33:33.360 --> 33:34.170
No.

33:38.780 --> 33:40.450
But I know where the antidote is.

33:41.980 --> 33:44.280
There's a hidden drawer in the cabinet on the east side of Zhen Yu's room.

33:45.010 --> 33:46.430
The antidote is in it.

33:48.200 --> 33:49.870
Are you really willing to tell me?

33:51.220 --> 33:53.240
I guess it's because you're like me-

33:54.380 --> 33:55.890
pitiful,

33:56.280 --> 33:57.240
ridiculous,

33:58.100 --> 33:59.090
despicable,

33:59.660 --> 34:00.500
and pathetic.

34:03.490 --> 34:06.400
You and I fight and struggle here in Cold Spring Palace,

34:06.920 --> 34:08.929
and we're each other's most hated enemies,

34:08.960 --> 34:10.280
but in the end,

34:10.820 --> 34:12.699
we're also each other's only companions.

34:14.550 --> 34:16.060
Whether you believe it or not,

34:16.310 --> 34:19.350
I've never once thought about truly taking your life.

34:20.000 --> 34:20.969
Fu Ling,

34:21.719 --> 34:22.810
just live

34:23.429 --> 34:24.800
if you can.

34:51.620 --> 34:52.330
What's wrong with you?

34:53.210 --> 34:54.920
I want to get more power as quickly as possible,

34:55.290 --> 34:56.360
but suddenly my chest

34:56.610 --> 34:57.820
feels a little tight.

34:57.930 --> 34:59.430
Now that the Four Contemplations are in your body

34:59.560 --> 35:00.860
and you've gained Bai Ze's spiritual power;

35:01.250 --> 35:03.170
these powers can help you become stronger,

35:03.190 --> 35:04.790
but you also need to find a way

35:04.820 --> 35:06.140
to cultivate them for your own use.

35:06.660 --> 35:07.660
Cultivate them?

35:16.320 --> 35:17.510
What is this place?

35:18.020 --> 35:20.290
After I was injured and left the Bai Ze Clan,

35:20.370 --> 35:22.100
I traveled everywhere to practice Demon Race techniques,

35:22.120 --> 35:23.390
all while thinking about revenge.

35:24.100 --> 35:25.620
Perhaps it was heaven's blessing

35:26.180 --> 35:27.610
that I accidentally stumbled upon this cave.

35:28.340 --> 35:29.820
Inside, there were many secret techniques.

35:29.850 --> 35:31.720
After cultivating them, my demonic power grew rapidly,

35:32.000 --> 35:33.610
and within three years, I had conquered the Eastern Continent.

35:33.970 --> 35:35.370
There's nothing in this cave.

35:35.400 --> 35:36.730
How could there be secret techniques

35:37.060 --> 35:39.500
that could increase your demonic power so quickly

35:39.530 --> 35:40.970
and help you conquer the Eastern Continent?

36:18.450 --> 36:21.240
Why isn't there any reaction when I touch the cave wall?

36:21.510 --> 36:22.590
Could it be that only you

36:22.590 --> 36:24.960
can make these images appear and disappear?

36:25.590 --> 36:27.170
I've always wondered.

36:28.090 --> 36:29.200
Maybe

36:30.030 --> 36:31.500
the only explanation I can think of

36:32.270 --> 36:33.870
is that I have the Demon Lord's Divine Mantle.

36:34.390 --> 36:35.280
This cave

36:35.490 --> 36:36.850
might be related to the Divine Race.

36:37.610 --> 36:38.680
The Divine Race?

36:39.230 --> 36:40.750
Back then, I cultivated haphazardly

36:40.780 --> 36:42.410
and accidentally created the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal,

36:43.750 --> 36:45.860
but I could never find a way to break it.

36:46.370 --> 36:47.850
Later, I saved Old Turtle,

36:47.870 --> 36:49.730
and from his divination, I learned that

36:49.770 --> 36:51.000
only the power of the Contemplation Stone

36:51.000 --> 36:52.560
could break the Seven Stars backlash.

36:52.580 --> 36:54.140
But the Contemplation Stone is a divine object,

36:54.320 --> 36:56.350
and no one knows its exact use.

36:56.890 --> 36:58.640
I only learned about the Contemplation Stone

36:58.790 --> 37:00.170
from these murals.

37:03.190 --> 37:04.310
What are you thinking?

37:04.590 --> 37:05.500
Nothing.

37:06.300 --> 37:07.780
I just feel like

37:08.050 --> 37:10.790
someone was secretly guiding you.

37:11.010 --> 37:12.530
First, he led you to this cave

37:12.560 --> 37:14.250
to cultivate the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal,

37:14.270 --> 37:16.460
then he arranged for you to search for the Contemplation Stone.

37:16.850 --> 37:18.320
What kind of mission

37:18.480 --> 37:20.560
does the Demon Lord's Divine Mantle carry on?

37:20.960 --> 37:22.310
Maybe when the time comes,

37:22.720 --> 37:24.070
everything will have an answer.

37:30.380 --> 37:31.190
What's wrong?

37:32.240 --> 37:33.340
I don't know.

37:34.130 --> 37:35.380
It's hard to explain.

37:35.710 --> 37:37.320
You have the Demon Lord's Divine Mantle,

37:38.370 --> 37:40.270
so naturally, you are destined for greatness.

37:40.120 --> 37:44.860
♫The white-haired elder lives in peaceful seclusion in the mountains♫

37:41.950 --> 37:43.320
But I've thought it through;

37:43.730 --> 37:45.570
no one can stop us from being together.

37:46.350 --> 37:51.490
♫The misty mountains, with rain washing away the dust♫

37:46.630 --> 37:47.800
Even if you are a deity,

37:48.400 --> 37:50.680
even if the deity has eternal life

37:51.000 --> 37:52.490
and omnipotent powers,

37:52.840 --> 37:58.970
♫A peaceful detachment, neither hearing nor asking♫

37:52.920 --> 37:54.140
so what?

37:54.160 --> 37:56.000
I will still hone my skills

37:56.790 --> 37:58.350
and make everyone know that

37:58.700 --> 37:59.730
I, Bai Shuo,

37:59.590 --> 38:04.910
♫No one needs to take these vain words seriously♫

37:59.770 --> 38:01.400
am worthy to stand shoulder to shoulder with the deity.

38:03.370 --> 38:04.550
How arrogant.

38:06.080 --> 38:09.430
♫I've climbed 3,000 steps with a sincere heart♫

38:07.330 --> 38:09.670
Didn't you know that when you first met me?

38:09.890 --> 38:11.640
Bai Shuo from Ning'an City

38:10.060 --> 38:13.450
♫I've prayed to the Buddha, burning incense, keeping to oneself♫

38:12.040 --> 38:13.290
is arrogant, conceited,

38:13.310 --> 38:14.490
and reckless.

38:14.120 --> 38:16.900
♫Don't ask, don't separate, don't describe the universe anymore♫

38:14.770 --> 38:16.550
Everyone says the deity is powerful,

38:16.970 --> 38:19.450
but I will claim you as my own.

38:17.390 --> 38:19.690
♫I only deserve to read poetry intoxicatingly♫

38:20.580 --> 38:23.630
♫I am an average person who fell into the mundane world♫

38:24.350 --> 38:27.230
♫Holding a lonely lamp to light up nirvana♫

38:28.060 --> 38:33.900
♫Don't approach, don't recognize, don't forget I'm not drifting♫

38:32.330 --> 38:34.290
This stone bed will help steady your mind

38:34.380 --> 38:37.760
♫I've climbed 3,000 steps with a sincere heart♫

38:34.540 --> 38:35.910
and prevent you from falling into demonic madness.

38:36.330 --> 38:38.700
First, try to channel the contemplation power and spiritual power inside you

38:38.400 --> 38:40.740
♫I've prayed to the Buddha, burning incense, keeping to oneself♫

38:38.730 --> 38:39.980
into the energy base,

38:40.590 --> 38:42.020
then slowly disperse it,

38:41.630 --> 38:44.400
♫Don't ask, don't separate, don't describe the universe anymore♫

38:42.050 --> 38:42.950
transforming it into

38:43.500 --> 38:45.410
a power you can control.

38:44.870 --> 38:47.300
♫I only deserve to read poetry intoxicatingly♫

38:46.310 --> 38:47.150
Remember,

38:47.180 --> 38:48.600
you must focus all your energy,

38:47.970 --> 38:51.590
♫I am an average person who fell into the mundane world♫

38:48.870 --> 38:50.280
with no distractions.

38:50.970 --> 38:52.700
I won't let anyone disturb you.

38:51.920 --> 38:54.670
♫Holding a lonely lamp to light up nirvana♫

38:55.250 --> 39:01.320
♫Don't approach, don't recognize, don't forget I'm not drifting♫

39:38.080 --> 39:39.470
There are countless demons,

39:39.490 --> 39:41.400
and you're neither the most talented

39:41.420 --> 39:42.840
nor the strongest.

39:42.870 --> 39:44.420
Why did he take you in

39:44.440 --> 39:45.520
and keep you by his side?

39:45.550 --> 39:46.790
Aren't you curious about

39:47.100 --> 39:48.910
who you were

39:49.470 --> 39:51.100
before becoming Fu Ling?

39:51.580 --> 39:54.140
Zhen Yu had already disregarded the fate of immortals and demons when he was in the Outlanders' City.

39:54.160 --> 39:56.280
What is the conspiracy he is now scheming?

40:05.410 --> 40:06.370
Master.

40:12.410 --> 40:13.290
What?

40:13.820 --> 40:14.890
Are you also

40:14.920 --> 40:16.080
going to betray me?

40:16.110 --> 40:17.960
I have never coveted the secret treasure.

40:18.180 --> 40:18.970
I was just

40:19.000 --> 40:20.250
momentarily confused

40:20.270 --> 40:21.780
and wanted to cure the Heart Devouring poison.

40:21.870 --> 40:23.120
Everything I have given you,

40:23.140 --> 40:24.050
all the blessings and hardships,

40:24.080 --> 40:25.210
are the my grace.

40:25.230 --> 40:26.760
Since when have you

40:27.350 --> 40:28.950
begun to

40:28.970 --> 40:30.490
go against my wishes?

40:30.510 --> 40:31.430
I dare not.

40:31.460 --> 40:32.460
You dare not?

40:32.940 --> 40:33.930
Didn't you

40:34.140 --> 40:35.220
meet with Chen Ye

40:35.250 --> 40:36.600
last night?

40:42.580 --> 40:43.970
I want to know

40:44.360 --> 40:45.590
do I still have family

40:45.610 --> 40:46.850
in this world?

40:47.530 --> 40:49.180
And before becoming Fu Ling,

40:49.530 --> 40:50.640
who was I?

40:53.920 --> 40:55.330
You want to know

40:55.360 --> 40:56.550
who you are?

40:58.000 --> 40:58.960
Fu Ling,

40:58.980 --> 41:00.200
it's been ten years

41:00.370 --> 41:02.300
since I

41:02.320 --> 41:03.680
brought you back to Cold Spring Palace.

41:05.970 --> 41:07.210
We've been master and disciple

41:07.550 --> 41:09.350
for ten years.

41:09.600 --> 41:11.160
I once taught you that

41:12.240 --> 41:14.280
people should look forward.

41:14.740 --> 41:16.100
Thinking too much

41:16.130 --> 41:17.000
will only

41:17.020 --> 41:18.780
make you die faster.

41:20.020 --> 41:21.410
Young Lord, watch out!

41:23.860 --> 41:24.970
Xixi!

41:25.420 --> 41:27.910
Young Lord, run!

41:28.390 --> 41:29.320
Let her go!

41:29.340 --> 41:30.380
Master.

41:30.410 --> 41:31.330
I'm begging you

41:31.360 --> 41:33.220
to let Xixi go.

41:34.200 --> 41:35.020
Young Lord!

41:39.760 --> 41:40.550
Xixi.

41:40.570 --> 41:41.530
Young Lord.

41:44.030 --> 41:44.980
No!

41:48.790 --> 41:50.060
Xixi!

42:04.480 --> 42:06.270
Come chase after me!

42:09.320 --> 42:11.070
This fabric looks great for making clothes.

42:11.100 --> 42:13.270
I think this would make a great cape.

42:13.290 --> 42:14.500
Yes, it's very beautiful.

42:14.550 --> 42:15.200
-Am I fast?
-Yes.

42:15.220 --> 42:16.550
A bit faster.

42:16.880 --> 42:17.730
Okay.

42:19.200 --> 42:21.020
Your handwriting is terrible.

42:20.270 --> 42:25.230
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

42:21.050 --> 42:22.780
Your handwriting is terrible.

42:23.630 --> 42:24.550
Didn't you say

42:24.550 --> 42:27.190
you would wait for Xi to come back with me?

42:27.190 --> 42:29.840
We still haven't waited for her yet.

42:28.390 --> 42:34.020
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

42:29.840 --> 42:31.340
You can't die!

42:36.680 --> 42:44.080
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

42:41.950 --> 42:43.480
Father.

42:45.030 --> 42:50.080
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

42:45.930 --> 42:47.480
I'm.

42:50.320 --> 42:51.690
Shuo?

42:52.490 --> 42:53.700
I'm not.

42:53.720 --> 42:54.510
No.

42:55.190 --> 42:56.830
I'm not.

42:56.850 --> 42:58.210
No, you are Shuo.

42:58.240 --> 42:59.390
I'm not.

42:59.410 --> 43:00.530
No.

43:00.560 --> 43:02.360
Since you've already remembered,

43:02.380 --> 43:04.190
why deny it?

43:04.510 --> 43:05.410
Am I right?

43:05.440 --> 43:07.000
My good disciple.

43:07.610 --> 43:08.690
Bai Xi.

43:10.030 --> 43:13.500
♫Across thousands of miles♫

43:11.300 --> 43:13.150
It was I who sent someone

43:13.180 --> 43:14.980
to take you away from Ning'an City back then,

43:15.010 --> 43:16.100
and it was I

43:16.120 --> 43:17.650
who erased your memories,

43:17.290 --> 43:22.550
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

43:17.670 --> 43:18.900
turning you from a human

43:18.930 --> 43:20.260
into a demon.

43:20.280 --> 43:22.760
Bai Xun was killed by your own hands.

43:23.150 --> 43:24.110
Bai Shuo,

43:24.140 --> 43:25.450
all the suffering you've endured

43:25.620 --> 43:27.370
has your involvement.

43:25.760 --> 43:32.710
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

43:28.040 --> 43:29.410
I'm not Bai Xi.

43:29.440 --> 43:30.540
I'm not!

43:30.770 --> 43:32.210
Since you're in so much pain,

43:32.230 --> 43:34.420
why not let me help you put an end to it?

43:33.710 --> 43:38.650
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

43:34.630 --> 43:35.500
After all,

43:35.530 --> 43:37.050
the one I've truly been looking for

43:37.070 --> 43:38.580
was never you.
